{"tid":576253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"考2019dse計劃 歡迎討論","createTime":"2018-02-28T17:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T22:06:41.000Z","uid":3465,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"becbb4b52ba246baa789ee03db826f7f98bf81f8","tid":576253,"uid":3465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T17:42:12.000Z","msg":"老老竇竇，其實自修生同日校生條curve分開拉<br />\n其實我地考得幾好都冇用<br />\n咁倒不如係試場攪下屎棍好過<br />\n<br />\n首先，最易玩野當然係Oral，壟斷發言或者不斷疊聲就ok，咁不過要注意唔可以玩得太盡，如果搗亂既話班dse雞係可以重考架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二值得玩野既就係Listening，呢份卷佔分重，玩起上嚟成效比Oral高。不過可以點玩呢？相信考過都知，其實監考佬係唔要點check你部機，各位大可以帶部有喇叭既機入去，睇睇下轉做啲鳩野，好似咩「佢家下黃色衫」、「少理呀爸」、「陳庭佳」之類，仲要大大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過，上述兩份卷都只係中英文有，都未算最盡。要真正玩鳩班00後，一定要玩埋大卷。我建議可以考大卷之前做下晨運，踢返場波，做下啲有益身心既運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一身大汗咁入去考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲可以帶啲咩臭魚罐頭咁入去開，臭死晒班00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又或者前一日食多啲野，考緊嗰陣係咁大大聲放屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 有冇人諗住真係組團去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後贈00後一句：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8637a27ba62c5f928dc779d76b9d14088c36e5b0","tid":576253,"uid":101253,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T17:44:32.000Z","msg":"入去訓教   <br />\n自問鼻寒大聲到全家人訓唔到"},{"pid":"7c300007387bf83237795aff9f626eb5d55adc1